            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Dol</abbr><ex>icheno</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Cla</abbr><ex>udius</ex></expan> Mate<lb break="no" n="3"/>rnus ex vo<lb break="no" n="4"/>to pro se <lb n="5"/>et suis <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Blattartiges Plättchen; Gewicht: 14,92 g. Inschriftfeld in Form einer tabula ansata; darüber ein Stern. Inschrift eingeritzt. Z. 6/7 verteilen sich auf die linke und rechte Hälfte eines nach unten zeigenden Dreiecks unterhalb der tabula ansata. (B): AE 1939: Z. 5 (Ende): VO.</p>
            </div>
